  "body": "**Describe the bug**\r\n\r\nI switched form a v1.2.0-rc.3 github deployment to docker:\r\n\r\n- Better validator performance\r\n\r\n<img width=\"815\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2022-11-06 at 14 25 11\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/10568965/200159174-6292f714-9c24-4228-bf08-4defa30e033c.png\">\r\n\r\n- Better gossip attestation validation\r\n\r\n<img width=\"812\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2022-11-06 at 14 25 53\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/10568965/200159197-f7c820bc-b92f-4861-82ca-13b6e9f4a9e6.png\">\r\n\r\n- Could be due to better BLS's performance\r\n\r\n<img width=\"807\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2022-11-06 at 14 27 24\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/10568965/200159258-00db8a94-e961-4eb3-8a10-79c11dbd8fbd.png\">\r\n\r\n\r\n- Less dropped messages\r\n\r\n<img width=\"782\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2022-11-06 at 14 26 31\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/10568965/200159219-1b4384e2-75db-4d9d-b7b4-cb0b0cf13ec4.png\">\r\n\r\n- Less time  / more stable epoch transition\r\n\r\n<img width=\"1207\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2022-11-06 at 14 37 08\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/10568965/200159526-aa9127ac-f7e4-47f9-8007-97db229393f3.png\">\r\n\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior**\r\n\r\nPerformance between 2 types of deployment should be the same",
